---
title: Spiced Cauliflower Mac 'N' Cheese with Mixed Greens
description: Although we love a gooey, stick-to-your-ribs sort of mac n’ cheese, sometimes you want a version that offers all of the same comforts but with a lighter, brighter feel to it. This recipe does just that, folding some crispy roasted cauliflower into the mix, adding a dash of warm North African spices, and introducing a cheese sauce that’s creamy without feeling weighed down. If the bright orange mac is an occasional treat, this is one you can enjoy any night of the week.
